<item>
            <title>[LU-14393] Batching Processing Framework for Lustre</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14393</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Batching processing can obtain boost performance. The larger the batch size, the higher the latency for the entire batch. Although the latency for the entire batch of operations is higher than the latency of any single operation, the throughput of the batch of operations is much higher.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket is used to track this new feature.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
